 drawrect ctl;xy;newxy;hgt;wid;loc;dim;newtop;newbottom;newleft;newright
 'f.rect'вЋ•WS('event' 'mousemove' 0)('event' 'mouseup' 0)
 xyв†ђ'f.rect2'вЋ•WG'points'
 newxyв†ђoffset+ctl[2 3]
 hgtв†ђnewxy[0]-xy[0]
 widв†ђ(Г—newxy[1]-xy[1])Г—вЊЉ4Г—|hgtГ·3
 'f.rect2'вЋ•WS('size'(hgt,wid))
 вЌќ:If 'Mandelbrot'YesNo'Draw new space?'
 loc dimв†ђ'f.rect2'вЋ•WG'points' 'size'
