 dimв†ђ|dim
 newtopв†ђtop-(top-bottom)Г—loc[0]Г·picdims[0]
 newbottomв†ђnewtop-(top-bottom)Г—dim[0]Г·picdims[0]
 newleftв†ђleft+(right-left)Г—loc[1]Г·picdims[1]
 newrightв†ђnewleft+4Г—(newtop-newbottom)Г·3
 topв†ђnewtop в‹„ bottomв†ђnewbottom в‹„ leftв†ђnewleft в‹„ rightв†ђnewright
 вЋ•EX'f.rect2'
